e (see Tips)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To save time, you can use fresh, peeled beetroots (and omit step 1). However, the ketchup will be grainy and earthy and will only keep in the refrigerator for up to 1 week.","You can store this ketchup in the refrigerator for up to 3 weeks."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 15m","1"]}